description: Set the configuration values for model invocation logging.

parameters.name: loggingConfig
parameters.description: The logging configuration values to set. cloudWatchConfig (dict) --- CloudWatch logging configuration. logGroupName (string) --- The log group name. roleArn (string) --- The role Amazon Resource Name (ARN). largeDataDeliveryS3Config (dict) --- S3 configuration for delivering a large amount of data. bucketName (string) --- S3 bucket name. keyPrefix (string) --- S3 prefix. s3Config (dict) --- S3 configuration for storing log data. textDataDeliveryEnabled (boolean) --- Set to include text data in the log delivery. imageDataDeliveryEnabled (boolean) --- Set to include image data in the log delivery. embeddingDataDeliveryEnabled (boolean) --- Set to include embeddings data in the log delivery. videoDataDeliveryEnabled (boolean) --- Set to include video data in the log delivery.
